1
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Why do you hate Lady Tiararose so?</font>

2
00:00:18,830 --> 00:00:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla is sad.</font>

3
00:00:20,720 --> 00:00:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes us sad, too.</font>

4
00:00:22,460 --> 00:00:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go bully that Tiararose lady 
who took her true love from her!</font>

5
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">Yeah!</font></font>

6
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it because I have feelings 
for Prince Aquasteed?</font>

7
00:00:34,750 --> 00:00:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you dare...</font>

8
00:00:36,850 --> 00:00:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">let the fact that you have 
the fairies' blessing</font>

9
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:40,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and were able to come here</font>

10
00:00:40,910 --> 00:00:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">get to your head!</font>

11
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm very sorry!</font>

12
00:00:50,990 --> 00:00:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incidentally, Icilla...</font>

13
00:00:53,290 --> 00:00:55,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you familiar with what 
goes on around Tiararose?</font>

14
00:00:56,410 --> 00:00:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, somewhat...</font>

15
00:00:58,730 --> 00:01:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then are you aware of 
Claire's current circumstances?</font>

16
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claire?</font>

17
00:01:04,210 --> 00:01:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry. I don't know who that is.</font>

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:12,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? After I opened the path 
for you to come here?</font>

19
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough. Leave me.</font>

20
00:01:29,230 --> 00:01:32,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he would come 
and have tea with me...</font>

21
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I just use this...</font>

22
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:58,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an2}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="28"><b><font color="#f76bb3">The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
<font color="#6b3e34">by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

23
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><b><font color="#f76bb3"><font size="25">Whisper</font></font></b> <font color="#6b3e34">That You <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Love</b> <font color="#6b3e34">Me</font></font></font></font></font>

24
00:03:21,820 --> 00:03:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you were able to meet 
the Sea Fairy King,</font>

25
00:03:24,790 --> 00:03:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you were immediately sent away?</font>

26
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

27
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't give up so soon, 
so I dove down several more times...</font>

28
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I was not allowed near 
the Fairy King's shrine again.</font>

29
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please try not to feel so bad.</font>

30
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:45,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cookies really aren't that important.</font>

31
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

32
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll see if I can sort this out by my—</font>

33
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claire?</font>

34
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to visit.</font>

35
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:04,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Claire!</font>

36
00:04:05,900 --> 00:04:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>King... Claire?</i></font>

37
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, you're just ignoring me?</font>

38
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:11,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keith!</font>

39
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:15,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard that you'd been having 
tea with Claire recently.</font>

40
00:04:16,610 --> 00:04:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while, Tiara.</font>

41
00:04:28,210 --> 00:04:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought you a lovely gift today.</font>

42
00:04:30,850 --> 00:04:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's coral tea.</font>

43
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You can make tea from coral?</i></font>

44
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:38,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the Sky Fairy King, 
yet you brought coral tea?</font>

45
00:04:38,970 --> 00:04:42,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. It's my favorite.</font>

46
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:46,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did get it from Pearl, though.</font>

47
00:04:46,690 --> 00:04:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's good, so I'm sharing it.</font>

48
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Pearl?</i></font>

49
00:04:55,570 --> 00:04:59,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has the fragrance of the sea 
and sweet flowers.</font>

50
00:04:59,350 --> 00:05:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it lovely?</font>

51
00:05:02,530 --> 00:05:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara is my wife. 
Don't get too close to her.</font>

52
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Aquasteed, you're no fun at all.</font>

53
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better keep a tight 
hold on her, or I'll take her.</font>

54
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keith! I only have eyes for Prince Aqua!</font>

55
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same goes for me.</font>

56
00:05:21,380 --> 00:05:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are head-over-heels 
for each other.</font>

57
00:05:25,350 --> 00:05:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I envy that.</font>

58
00:05:42,370 --> 00:05:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's...</i></font>

59
00:05:47,170 --> 00:05:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I might get to see you 
if I used coral tea.</font>

60
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Claire, who is that?</font>

61
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:57,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. You two haven't 
met her yet, have you?</font>

62
00:05:58,820 --> 00:06:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Pearl, the Sea Fairy King.</font>

63
00:06:06,330 --> 00:06:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you so angry about, Pearl?</font>

64
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come, now. 
You need to return their greeting.</font>

65
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do not give me orders!</font>

66
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just look at you, 
a <i>man</i> dressing that way!</font>

67
00:06:17,410 --> 00:06:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pearl...</font>

68
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What? King Claire is a man?</i></font>

69
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should expect no less 
of the fairy kings.</i></font>

70
00:06:24,450 --> 00:06:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're all such unique individuals!</i></font>

71
00:06:27,340 --> 00:06:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't believe all three of them 
are here at once!</i></font>

72
00:06:36,130 --> 00:06:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claire, you fool!</font>

73
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pearl said she hated men,</font>

74
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I started dressing like this in hopes 
that we could be friends.</font>

75
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You favor Pearl that much?</font>

76
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But surely just dressing like a woman 
won't make her like you.</font>

77
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:01,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, but it was 
the only way I could think of.</font>

78
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Claire...</font>

79
00:07:03,580 --> 00:07:05,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shh, Tiara.</font>

80
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We humans mustn't try to interfere 
in the fairy kings' affairs carelessly.</font>

81
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

82
00:07:14,580 --> 00:07:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure his idea that 
she hates him is a mistake.</i></font>

83
00:07:17,370 --> 00:07:20,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll feel so bad for them 
if their misunderstanding continues.</i></font>

84
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Also, if Keith knew that, 
he should've said so!</i></font>

85
00:07:29,260 --> 00:07:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I won't give up.</font>

86
00:07:32,150 --> 00:07:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll just keep closing the distance 
between Pearl and me little by little.</font>

87
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah? Good luck with that.</font>

88
00:07:39,650 --> 00:07:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I know. Maybe 
I'll give her some sort of gift.</font>

89
00:07:43,580 --> 00:07:47,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you mind going shopping 
with me sometime soon?</font>

90
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what would 
make a good gift for a girl.</font>

91
00:07:51,180 --> 00:07:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you think I can help, I would love to!</font>

92
00:08:00,470 --> 00:08:03,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't think King Pearl 
hates King Claire at all.</i></font>

93
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm almost certain 
she actually likes him.</i></font>

94
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did seeing me enjoy tea time with 
the other kings make King Pearl upset?</font>

95
00:08:15,020 --> 00:08:16,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

96
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Y-Y-You're kidding!</font>

97
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Sea Fairy King came here in person?!</font>

98
00:08:20,690 --> 00:08:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you plotting?</font>

99
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

100
00:08:23,780 --> 00:08:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that tea party for?</font>

101
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:27,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

102
00:08:27,150 --> 00:08:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trying to win the fairy kings over 
with tasty sweets?</font>

103
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You obviously have ulterior motives!</font>

104
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then would you like to join us 
at our next tea party?</font>

105
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you saying?!</font>

106
00:08:38,670 --> 00:08:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As if I would ever have tea 
with the likes of you!</font>

107
00:08:42,370 --> 00:08:44,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll invite King Claire, too.</font>

108
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Claire seemed very eager 
to see you again.</font>

109
00:08:49,780 --> 00:08:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As I said—</font>

110
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know it'll be fun!</font>

111
00:08:52,470 --> 00:08:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't invite a fairy king 
over for tea so casually!</font>

112
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Know your place!</font>

113
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:58,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll let this go for today,</font>

114
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:02,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if you make things any worse, 
I have some ideas of my own!</font>

115
00:09:02,190 --> 00:09:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Pearl, I—</font>

116
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silence! I am the Sea Fairy King! 
Do not defy me!</font>

117
00:09:07,780 --> 00:09:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And do not get any closer 
to the kings—to Claire!</font>

118
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Claire...</font>

119
00:09:22,530 --> 00:09:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

120
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter?</font>

121
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't go with you to choose 
a gift for King Pearl.</font>

122
00:09:33,490 --> 00:09:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not?</font>

123
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't want to anymore?</font>

124
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When choosing a gift 
for a woman you like,</font>

125
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:51,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think it's wise to go shopping 
for it with another woman.</font>

126
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The young maiden in me</font>

127
00:09:54,050 --> 00:09:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would want such a gift to be chosen 
personally by the man buying it.</font>

128
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:06,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure she'll be happier 
with a gift you chose yourself.</font>

129
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's what a maiden's 
heart desires, is it?</font>

130
00:10:15,130 --> 00:10:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, I'll try shopping on my own.</font>

131
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:20,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Tiararose.</font>

132
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you looking for a gift?</font>

133
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's right.</font>

134
00:10:55,380 --> 00:10:58,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was thinking of something 
made with coral.</font>

135
00:10:58,160 --> 00:11:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And for the color... I'm not sure...</font>

136
00:11:01,050 --> 00:11:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Red is beautiful,</font>

137
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the colors of the sky 
and sea are lovely, too.</font>

138
00:11:09,060 --> 00:11:11,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one is nice. I'll take it.</font>

139
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

140
00:11:14,770 --> 00:11:16,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope she'll like it.</font>

141
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, goodness! These are adorable!</font>

142
00:11:20,430 --> 00:11:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'd suit Tiararose perfectly!</font>

143
00:11:24,100 --> 00:11:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since we've gotten 
to be such good friends,</font>

144
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">maybe I'll buy matching ones.</font>

145
00:11:34,980 --> 00:11:36,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claire...</font>

146
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He looks so happy about this...</font>

147
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The seas are getting rough?</font>

148
00:11:54,290 --> 00:11:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pearl, what's wrong?</font>

149
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:04,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world is going on?</font>

150
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="24"><b>The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

151
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must inform Prince Aquasteed right away!</font>

152
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla!</font>

153
00:12:23,970 --> 00:12:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla, the king is angry!</font>

154
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:29,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fairy king? What has happened?</font>

155
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's angry! She's angry!</font>

156
00:12:31,730 --> 00:12:33,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's <i>super</i> angry!</font>

157
00:12:33,730 --> 00:12:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. Don't go acting on your own.</font>

158
00:12:41,110 --> 00:12:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King!</font>

159
00:12:43,490 --> 00:12:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph. I dislike 
the woman called Tiararose.</font>

160
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:48,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She has some nerve leading Claire on.</font>

161
00:12:50,290 --> 00:12:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lady Tiararose did that?</i></font>

162
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:57,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla, you must take Aquasteed 
away from Tiararose.</font>

163
00:12:57,300 --> 00:12:58,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

164
00:13:05,530 --> 00:13:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

165
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The secret elixir of the sea.</font>

166
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Secret elixir?</font>

167
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:15,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. If you add one 
drop of your blood to it</font>

168
00:13:15,590 --> 00:13:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and make Aquasteed drink it,</font>

169
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:20,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">his heart will belong to you.</font>

170
00:13:22,650 --> 00:13:25,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His heart? Then this is...</font>

171
00:13:26,290 --> 00:13:27,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a love potion?</font>

172
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So with this...</i></font>

173
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:35,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could make Prince Aquasteed love me?</i></font>

174
00:13:36,580 --> 00:13:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know it's wrong.</i></font>

175
00:13:38,810 --> 00:13:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't just toy with Prince Aquasteed's 
feelings however I please.</i></font>

176
00:13:44,370 --> 00:13:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

177
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pearl!</font>

178
00:13:54,830 --> 00:13:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claire!</font>

179
00:13:56,950 --> 00:13:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world is wrong?</font>

180
00:14:00,220 --> 00:14:02,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have nothing to say to you!</font>

181
00:14:03,850 --> 00:14:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

182
00:14:05,740 --> 00:14:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, darn it. She just 
won't listen to a word I say.</font>

183
00:14:16,370 --> 00:14:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lift your head, Icilla Pearllant.</font>

184
00:14:20,490 --> 00:14:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me what has happened to Pearl.</font>

185
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Pearl said that Lady Tiararose 
is leading you on.</font>

186
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leading me on? That's ridiculous.</font>

187
00:14:33,410 --> 00:14:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

188
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just what does Pearl think
 is happening here?</font>

189
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's clear how much Tiararose 
and Aquasteed love each other.</font>

190
00:14:56,060 --> 00:15:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blessings of the forest, please 
share a bit of your power with me.</font>

191
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:05,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since I've received Keith's blessing,</i></font>

192
00:15:05,730 --> 00:15:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>my magic has made a lot of progress.</i></font>

193
00:15:08,530 --> 00:15:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Putting my magic into my sweets 
seems to make them taste even better.</i></font>

194
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:18,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's very cute!</font>

195
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Prince Aquasteed, isn't it?</font>

196
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:24,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. I thought 
I'd make iced cookies of everyone.</font>

197
00:15:28,340 --> 00:15:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next is King Claire.</font>

198
00:15:33,530 --> 00:15:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder if he was able to buy that gift.</i></font>

199
00:15:42,730 --> 00:15:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">K-King Pearl?!</font>

200
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You... That...</font>

201
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:52,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that meant to be in Claire's image?!</font>

202
00:15:52,010 --> 00:15:53,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This is...</font>

203
00:15:55,450 --> 00:15:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all those times I warned you, 
you mean to continue leading him on?!</font>

204
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're wrong! I'm making 
cookies of everyone!</font>

205
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't just make one 
for King Claire alone!</font>

206
00:16:09,410 --> 00:16:14,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, just enjoy your fun 
while you still can.</font>

207
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

208
00:16:16,530 --> 00:16:20,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soon you will feel 
the same pain that I feel.</font>

209
00:16:28,410 --> 00:16:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Tiararose...</font>

210
00:16:33,940 --> 00:16:36,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sea remains murky and black.</font>

211
00:16:36,830 --> 00:16:40,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like we have no choice 
but to see Claire and the Sea Fairy King.</font>

212
00:16:40,760 --> 00:16:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Elliot and I will go on horseback.</font>

213
00:16:43,040 --> 00:16:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara and Lady Icilla, 
please follow us in a carriage.</font>

214
00:16:46,350 --> 00:16:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make arrangements right away.</font>

215
00:16:49,310 --> 00:16:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Soon you will feel 
the same pain that I feel.</i></font>

216
00:16:54,710 --> 00:16:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What did she mean by that?</i></font>

217
00:17:01,150 --> 00:17:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua...</font>

218
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be all right.</font>

219
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

220
00:17:10,820 --> 00:17:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla, is something wrong?</font>

221
00:17:14,110 --> 00:17:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No...</font>

222
00:17:19,910 --> 00:17:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have tea!</font>

223
00:17:23,270 --> 00:17:27,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At a time like this, the best thing 
to do is calm our minds.</font>

224
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll help you.</font>

225
00:17:34,900 --> 00:17:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Water of life, come forth.</font>

226
00:17:43,540 --> 00:17:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Thank you, Lady Icilla!</font>

227
00:17:47,150 --> 00:17:51,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. This is really 
the only way I can be of use.</font>

228
00:17:51,050 --> 00:17:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That isn't true.</font>

229
00:17:54,130 --> 00:17:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla, you are 
a fine caretaker of the seas.</font>

230
00:17:59,270 --> 00:18:01,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm not.</font>

231
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't stop the sea 
from turning black.</font>

232
00:18:07,530 --> 00:18:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you went down to the ocean floor</font>

233
00:18:09,570 --> 00:18:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">hoping to do something 
about it, didn't you?</font>

234
00:18:12,130 --> 00:18:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even when the Sea Fairy King stopped you, 
you tried over and over.</font>

235
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't give up.</font>

236
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that same way, you have 
done everything in your power</font>

237
00:18:20,710 --> 00:18:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for both the seas and the kingdom 
for all these years.</font>

238
00:18:24,350 --> 00:18:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that well.</font>

239
00:18:27,050 --> 00:18:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed...</font>

240
00:18:31,850 --> 00:18:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you are, Prince Aqua.</font>

241
00:18:35,580 --> 00:18:37,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Tiara.</font>

242
00:18:42,210 --> 00:18:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you add one drop of your blood to it</i></font>

243
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and make Aquasteed drink it,</i></font>

244
00:18:46,580 --> 00:18:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>his heart will belong to you.</i></font>

245
00:18:49,900 --> 00:18:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince...</i></font>

246
00:18:58,410 --> 00:19:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Aquasteed...</i></font>

247
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:07,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Aquasteed!</i></font>

248
00:19:13,260 --> 00:19:14,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

249
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:17,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla, eat with us.</font>

250
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Tiararose...</font>

251
00:19:22,140 --> 00:19:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll think about what we can do next, too.</font>

252
00:19:26,090 --> 00:19:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's try our hardest together.</font>

253
00:19:35,990 --> 00:19:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! Please don't drink that tea,</font>

254
00:19:39,740 --> 00:19:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed!</font>

255
00:19:44,950 --> 00:19:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Lady Icilla?</font>

256
00:19:49,860 --> 00:19:51,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

257
00:19:54,010 --> 00:19:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry... I... I...</font>

258
00:19:58,520 --> 00:20:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I put the secret elixir of the sea 
in Prince Aquasteed's tea!</font>

259
00:20:04,610 --> 00:20:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Secret elixir of the sea?</font>

260
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's a love potion.</font>

261
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:10,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

262
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never would have imagined...</i></font>

263
00:20:24,020 --> 00:20:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't cry, Icilla.</font>

264
00:20:31,190 --> 00:20:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Low and sweet... The same 
voice he uses to talk to me...</i></font>

265
00:20:39,110 --> 00:20:40,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla.</font>

266
00:20:47,940 --> 00:20:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed!</font>

267
00:20:50,270 --> 00:20:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to the sea, correct?</font>

268
00:20:53,090 --> 00:20:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. 
I'll take Icilla there first.</font>

269
00:20:57,900 --> 00:21:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sea fairies love Icilla,</font>

270
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so she should go with me.</font>

271
00:21:03,450 --> 00:21:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Prince Aqua...</font>

272
00:21:06,950 --> 00:21:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Tiara, you can wait here 
at the castle if you want.</font>

273
00:21:14,050 --> 00:21:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. It's because of the drug.</i></font>

274
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The usual Prince Aqua would never...</i></font>

275
00:21:21,220 --> 00:21:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come,</font>

276
00:21:23,830 --> 00:21:25,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla.</font>

277
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:31,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No! Please!</i></font>

278
00:21:31,580 --> 00:21:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't touch anyone but me!</i></font>

279
00:21:37,390 --> 00:21:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed...</font>

280
00:21:45,780 --> 00:21:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How long will the gods keep 
putting me through these trials?</i></font>

281
00:21:52,890 --> 00:21:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stop! Look at me!</i></font>

282
00:21:56,350 --> 00:21:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Aqua!</i></font>

283
00:23:29,970 --> 00:23:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="25"><font color="#6b3e34">My <b><font color="#f76bb3">Beautiful <font color="#3d8afc">Lady</font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

284
00:23:29,970 --> 00:23:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="25"><font color="#6b3e34">My <b><font color="#f76bb3">Beautiful <font color="#3d8afc">Lady</font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

285
00:23:30,730 --> 00:23:34,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara, you taught me what 
a joy it is to love.</font>

286
00:23:34,810 --> 00:23:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must convey these feelings now...</font>

287
00:23:36,520 --> 00:23:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to you, one who is like a flower.</font>

